# ShowUp — Frontend

## Layout

- Pages: `client/src/pages/`; shared UI: `client/src/components/`
- API modules: `client/src/api/{domain}.js` using `client/src/api/axios.js`
- Auth: `AuthContext` + `client/src/lib/authStorage.js` (JWT in localStorage)

## Patterns

- Functional components; local `useState`/`useEffect` — no global store
- API helpers check `success` and throw on failure; pages catch and display errors
- Route guards: `UserRoute` (blocks admins from `/submit`), `AdminRoute` (admin only)
- Dev proxy: Vite forwards `/api` to port 4000; paths use `/api/v1/...`
- Tailwind v4 via Vite plugin; minimal UI; reuse `components/Layout/`

## UI

- Prioritize functionality over polish
- Reuse existing card, form, and layout components before adding new ones
